{"tid":1671523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那出席唔到國際太空大會! 因簽證問題缺席","createTime":"2019-10-23T13:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T14:24:09.000Z","uid":14918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11f21166d4a5ea23fc044f3f97906219505ef59a","tid":1671523,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"國際太空大會中國代表團因簽證問題缺席<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】國際太空大會在美國華盛頓召開，原定與會的中國代表團缺席。在北京，外交部證實是由於美方未有及時發出簽證，批評美國將簽證武器化。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人華春瑩：「一段時間以來，美方對於中方的學者、學生、企業界人士、科技人員等赴美頻頻採取拒簽、拖延簽證申請、吊銷赴美長期簽證及盤查騷擾等措施，阻撓中美之間正常的人文交流與人員往來，損害了中方人員的安全與合法權益。美方把簽證問題武器化，一再藐視國際責任和義務，阻礙正常的國際交流和合作。<span style=\"color: red;\">我們敦促美方認真的反省、切實的改正</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫班官拎自己私伙護照咪得囉"},{"pid":"b852344daf8d09974da4b4bc024658a98f129d02","tid":1671523,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:55:53.000Z","msg":"咁你咪唔好黎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc0a400a7307c2ddcbb1997a8cc4ac8dcd2a1c8","tid":1671523,"uid":322508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:56:23.000Z","msg":"推行動POST唔該大佬...<br />\n<br />\n最新 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主線</span></span></strong> 日程表  (未能收納全部，請見諒。)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MWU0S5O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMWU0S5O.png&h=e01304d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUavpbD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUavpbD.jpg&h=5efe45aa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nu5LjKK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnu5LjKK.jpg&h=0b0ebc02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpjsx4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h